      <title>k近邻算法介绍及Python实现</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/18/k%E8%BF%91%E9%82%BB%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%E5%8F%8APython%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/18/k%E8%BF%91%E9%82%BB%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%E5%8F%8APython%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="k近邻算法介绍"><a href="#k近邻算法介绍" class="headerlink" title="k近邻算法介绍"></a>k近邻算法介绍</h1><h2 id="什么是k近邻算法？"><a href="#什么是k近邻算法？" class="headerlink" title="什么是k近邻算法？"></a>什么是k近邻算法？</h2><p>　　k近邻算法，即k-Nearest Neighbor，简称<strong>kNN</strong>算法，后续内容中，我们称其为<strong>kNN</strong>算法。<strong>kNN</strong>算法适合解决分类问题，其中<strong>k</strong>表示距离测试样本最近的<strong>k</strong>个样本数据。找到这k个样本数据中数量最多的一类，作为最后分类的结果。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="kNN算法的特点"><a href="#kNN算法的特点" class="headerlink" title="kNN算法的特点"></a>kNN算法的特点</h2><p>　　kNN算法是典型的<strong>非参数</strong>学习算法，即在学习过程中无任何参数。很明显，在kNN算法中，数据即模型。kNN算法天然可以解决多回归问题。  </p><p>​        kNN算法思想简单，实现起来也不复杂，但通过实现具体算法代码，我们需要掌握的是常规机器学习算法实现及常规从<strong>原始数据</strong>到<strong>训练模型</strong>再到<strong>评价模型好坏</strong>的全流程。  </p><h2 id="kNN算法的流程"><a href="#kNN算法的流程" class="headerlink" title="kNN算法的流程"></a>kNN算法的流程</h2><ol><li>计算测试数据到训练数据的距离</li><li>将距离进行排序，并取出前k个训练数据</li><li>将k个训练数据对应到类别，计算每个类别的个数</li><li>找到最大个数的类别，作为算法的返回值</li></ol><h2 id="相关概念"><a href="#相关概念" class="headerlink" title="相关概念"></a>相关概念</h2><p>　　和kNN有关的一个重要概念是：<strong>超参数</strong>。所谓超参数，就是在学习算法运行之前需要决定的参数，与之对应的是模型参数，模型参数是指在算法学习过程中的参数。因为kNN算法只需在算法运行前，给定k值和数据，就可以进行分类预测，所以，kNN算法没有模型参数。</p><p>　　我们如何寻找合适的超参数呢？常用方法有：<strong>领域知识、经验积累、实验搜索</strong>，由于在初学阶段，不能使用前面两种方法，<strong>实验搜索</strong>便是更适合初学者的方法。</p><p>　　其实，kNN算法不止k值这一个超参数，这将在后面的实现中进一步讨论。</p><h1 id="kNN算法实现"><a href="#kNN算法实现" class="headerlink" title="kNN算法实现"></a>kNN算法实现</h1><h2 id="算法核心实现"><a href="#算法核心实现" class="headerlink" title="算法核心实现"></a>算法核心实现</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 变量定义：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># X_train, y_train: 分别表示训练数据的特征和标签，数据类型均为ndarray</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># x：单个测试样本</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义距离数组，使用列表解析计算测试样本到训练数据的距离</span></span><br><span class="line">distances = np.array([np.sqrt(np.sum((x_trian - x)**<span class="number">2</span>)) <span class="keyword">for</span> x_train <span class="keyword">in</span> X_train])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 找到距离数组中值最小的k个值</span></span><br><span class="line">nearest = np.argsort(distances)[:k]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 对应的k个样本类别</span></span><br><span class="line">top_k_y = [y_train[i] <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> nearest]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 统计各个类别数量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> collections <span class="keyword">import</span> Counter</span><br><span class="line">votes = Counter(top_k_y)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获得结果</span></span><br><span class="line">y_predict = votes.most_common(<span class="number">1</span>)[<span class="number">0</span>][<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>　　上述代码中，x即为我们需要预测的数据，y_predict即为算法给出的结果。</p><h2 id="封装kNN算法"><a href="#封装kNN算法" class="headerlink" title="封装kNN算法"></a>封装kNN算法</h2><p>　　2.1中介绍的算法，只适合<strong>单个测试</strong>数据的测试，显然，这样是很不方便我们调用的，所以将算法封装到一个类中，提供方便用户使用的接口，才是更合理的做法。用户只需要给接口提供<strong>训练数据</strong>和<strong>相应的k值</strong>（甚至k值也可以默认，不需要用户传递参数），然后再给出<strong>需要分类的数据</strong>，即可获得结果。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># kNN.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> collections <span class="keyword">import</span> Counter</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">KNNClassifier</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">__init__</span><span class="params">(self, k)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.k = k</span><br><span class="line">        self._X_train = <span class="literal">None</span></span><br><span class="line">        self._y_train = <span class="literal">None</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 训练模型，kNN中，数据即模型</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">fit</span><span class="params">(self, X_train, y_train)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">assert</span> len(X_train) == len(y_train), <span class="string">"the length of X and y must be equal"</span></span><br><span class="line">        self._X_train = X_train</span><br><span class="line">        self._y_train = y_train</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> self</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 用模型进行预测，这里进行封装，可以一次预测多个数据。即用户接口</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">predict</span><span class="params">(self, X_predict)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">assert</span> _X_train <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="literal">None</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> _y_train <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="literal">None</span>, <span class="string">"must fit before predict!"</span></span><br><span class="line">        y_predict = [self._predict(x) <span class="keyword">for</span> x <span class="keyword">in</span> X_predict]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> np.array(y_predict)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 上述2.1节核心代码</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">_predict</span><span class="params">(self, x)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        distances = [np.sqrt(np.sum((x_train - x) ** <span class="number">2</span>)) <span class="keyword">for</span> x_train <span class="keyword">in</span> self._X_train]</span><br><span class="line">        topK_y = self._y_train[np.argsort(distances)[:self.k]]</span><br><span class="line">        votes = Counter(topK_y)</span><br><span class="line">        predict_y = votes.most_common(<span class="number">1</span>)[<span class="number">0</span>][<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> predict_y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="调用我们的kNN算法"><a href="#调用我们的kNN算法" class="headerlink" title="调用我们的kNN算法"></a>调用我们的kNN算法</h2><p>　　为了调用我们的kNN算法，我们使用封装在<code>sklearn</code>中的数据集：鸢尾花数据集。鸢尾花数据集封装在<code>sklearn.datasets</code>中，通过调用<code>load_iris()</code>函数即可加载数据。</p><p>　　在调用我们的算法之前，我们还需要做的是切分我们的数据集。将数据集划分为<strong>训练数据集</strong>和<strong>测试数据集</strong>，用训练数据集训练出模型，用测试数据集测试模型的好坏。如何划分数据集呢？我们可以自己实现随机划分的函数。但在这里，为了演示方便，使用<code>sklearn.model_selection</code>中的<code>train_test_split</code>函数，对数据集进行划分。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># main.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.model_selection <span class="keyword">import</span> train_test_split</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn <span class="keyword">import</span> datasets</span><br><span class="line">iris = datasets.load_iris()</span><br><span class="line">X = iris.data<span class="comment"># 特征矩阵</span></span><br><span class="line">y = iris.target<span class="comment"># 标签矩阵，即类别</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># train_test_split的参数详见官方文档</span></span><br><span class="line">X_train,X_test,y_train,y_test = train_test_split(X,y,test_size = <span class="number">0.2</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>　　有了数据后，就可以很方便的调用我们自己实现的kNN算法了：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># main.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> kNN <span class="keyword">import</span> KNNClassifier<span class="comment"># 导入我们实现的kNN分类器</span></span><br><span class="line">kNN_classifier = KNNClassifier(<span class="number">4</span>)<span class="comment"># k = 4</span></span><br><span class="line">kNN_classifier.fit(X_train,y_train)<span class="comment"># 训练模型</span></span><br><span class="line">y_predict = kNN_classifier.predict(X_test)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="评价我们的kNN算法"><a href="#评价我们的kNN算法" class="headerlink" title="评价我们的kNN算法"></a>评价我们的kNN算法</h2><p>　　上述2.3中的调用，似乎很方便的得到了预测结果，但是，我们不知道我们预测的分类结果是否准确，或者说，我们不知道我们的kNN算法的模型是否具有很好的预测效果。为了评价学习模型，我们有<strong>分类精确度</strong>的概念，即在测试数据集上，我们预测正确的数量与测试数据集总量的比值。</p><p>　　在<code>sklearn</code>中，评价标准一般封装在<code>metrics.py</code>中。所以，评价kNN算法的标准我们也创建在<code>metrics.py</code>中：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># metrices.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">accuracy_score</span><span class="params">(y_true, y_predict)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> sum(y_predict == y_true) / len(y_true)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>　　同时，在kNN分类器中，也定义一个函数，可以直接通过测试数据集得到分类精确度。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># kNN.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> .metrics <span class="keyword">import</span> accuracy_score</span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">KNNClassifier</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#...</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#...</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">score</span><span class="params">(self, X_test, y_test)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        y_predict = self.predict(X_test)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> accuracy_score(y_test,y_predict)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#...</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>　　通过这样的封装，用户可以根据是否需要知道预测值与否，来评价分类器的好坏。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># main.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 先求得预测值，再计算准确度</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> .metrics <span class="keyword">import</span> accuracy_score</span><br><span class="line">y_predict = kNN_classifier.predict(X_test)</span><br><span class="line">accuracy_score(y_test,y_predict)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或直接计算精确度</span></span><br><span class="line">kNN_classifier.score(X_test,y_test)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="调用sklearn中的kNN算法"><a href="#调用sklearn中的kNN算法" class="headerlink" title="调用sklearn中的kNN算法"></a>调用sklearn中的kNN算法</h1><h2 id="直接简单调用"><a href="#直接简单调用" class="headerlink" title="直接简单调用"></a>直接简单调用</h2><h2 id="调用sklearn中的评价标准"><a href="#调用sklearn中的评价标准" class="headerlink" title="调用sklearn中的评价标准"></a>调用sklearn中的评价标准</h2><h2 id="更多关于kNN的超参数"><a href="#更多关于kNN的超参数" class="headerlink" title="更多关于kNN的超参数"></a>更多关于kNN的超参数</h2><h3 id="有关距离的超参数"><a href="#有关距离的超参数" class="headerlink" title="有关距离的超参数"></a>有关距离的超参数</h3><h3 id="有关CPU核数与输出信息的超参数"><a href="#有关CPU核数与输出信息的超参数" class="headerlink" title="有关CPU核数与输出信息的超参数"></a>有关CPU核数与输出信息的超参数</h3><h2 id="如何获取最佳超参数"><a href="#如何获取最佳超参数" class="headerlink" title="如何获取最佳超参数"></a>如何获取最佳超参数</h2><h1 id="kNN中的数据处理"><a href="#kNN中的数据处理" class="headerlink" title="kNN中的数据处理"></a>kNN中的数据处理</h1><h2 id="为什么要进行数据处理"><a href="#为什么要进行数据处理" class="headerlink" title="为什么要进行数据处理"></a>为什么要进行数据处理</h2><h2 id="最值归一化"><a href="#最值归一化" class="headerlink" title="最值归一化"></a>最值归一化</h2><h2 id="均值方差归一化"><a href="#均值方差归一化" class="headerlink" title="均值方差归一化"></a>均值方差归一化</h2><h1 id="小结"><a href="#小结" class="headerlink" title="小结"></a>小结</h1>]]></content>
      
      
